 The UI of the app consists of:
- A menu bar with the app name "Studies" on the left and a close button on the right
- A navigation bar with a back button, a forward button, a refresh button, and a search bar
- A main view that is a scrollable list of study schedules. Each schedule has a title, a date, and a time.
- A note-taking section on the right that is initially hidden. It consists of a text editor and a save button.
- A control bar at the bottom with a play button, a pause button, a stop button, and a volume control.